Deji Elumoye in Abuja President Muhammadu Buhari who arrived the venue of the national convention of the ruling All Progressives Congress (APC) is about now meeting with the Interim National Chairman of the party, Mao Buni and the leadership of the National Assembly. Upon entering the VIP stand after the recitation of the National Anthem, the President after waving to top notchers of the party, proceeded to a room to confer with Buni, Senate President Ahmed Lawan and House Speaker Femi Gbajabiamila. Details later..